configure 0.0.2 release notes
-----------------------------

configure automatically generates Makefiles from project definition files.

configure is Copyright (c) 2005 Pierre Pronchery
It is shipped under the terms of the GPL version 2 license, which you may read
on the GNU project web site, http://www.gnu.org/ .

Please read the INSTALL file for instructions about how to compile and install
configure.

Please read the BUGS file for information about known problems, and planned
feature upgrades.

Please read the configure.txt file for information about how to use configure.

Thanks for using this program. I hope it will be useful.
